casebody.data:
Chase Carmen HUNTER, petitioner,
v.
Mitchel KALMANSON, et al. No. 13-6047. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2013.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until November 5, 2013, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in *468compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
